data.text:
The Adventures Of Abney & Teal, Episode 02 - The Star Stick

Series Synopsis

Follow the adventures of Abney and Teal, two friends who live on an island and whose lives are full of discovery and exploration. They are joined by their unique set of friends: Neep, Bop, Toby Dog and the playful Poc-Pocs.

Episode Synopsis

Episode 02 - The Star Stick

Teal can't sleep and is watching the sky when she sees a beautiful shooting star. She wakes up Abney and the Poc-Pocs to help her catch one for herself.
